# Invariants (repository hygiene — not storefront runtime):
# - Theme text (Liquid/JSON/JS/CSS) must use LF so Linux CI + Theme Check match editor output on Windows/macOS.
# - Binary assets must never be CRLF-normalized (prevents corrupt images/fonts).
# - Tooling/config (YAML, Node test scripts) must stay LF for deterministic CI and code review.
# Note: add-to-cart / fetch timeouts / Liquid null-safety live in theme source, not in this file.

* text=auto

*.liquid text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.scss text eol=lf
*.svg text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.cjs text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.eot binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
